Entrar al módulo y ejecutar:
```bash
cd /repositorios/tiddly-data-converter/go/bridge
mkdir -p ../../out
go run ./cmd/export_tiddlers \
  --html "../../data/tiddly-data-converter (Saved).html" \
  --out  "../../out/tiddlers.jsonl" \
  --log  "../../out/export.log" \
  --manifest "../../out/manifest.json"
```

Construir el binario y ejecutarlo:
```bash
cd /repositorios/tiddly-data-converter/go/bridge
go build -o export_tiddlers ./cmd/export_tiddlers
./export_tiddlers --html "../../data/tiddly-data-converter (Saved).html" --out "../../out/tiddlers.jsonl"
```

Crear un workspace Go que incluya los módulos
```bash
cd /repositorios/tiddly-data-converter
go run ./go/bridge/cmd/export_tiddlers \
  --html "data/tiddly-data-converter (Saved).html" \
  --out  "out/tiddlers.jsonl"
```

